{
  "stem": "1975.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, look, I'm not going to announce or tell anybody except these guys, this friend of mine, that you're escapee.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at night time, next day, they might join you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they have some-- they have knives and they have some other things to defending.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she brought me a knife also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And about a day and a half or two days later, came two Russian POWs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we have identified our self, and they told us they are going to-- they know-- they had a little map, handmade map.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said that I should follow them if I wanted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was-- a little by little, during the night time, we used to go watching our self, because during the day was very dangerous, you know, and especially in the morning time, when the sun came out.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We moved for about three days and we reached the forest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There, one of them had a assignment ready, apparently.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were also-- we met there a group of people who were, first of all, freedom fighters, who were very much concerned about us because they-- every time they see new faces, they were suspicious that should not be some Germans spies or anything.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there is where we met Vladimir, who was actually in charge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he told us that in the next day or something, we're going to get some supplies, and that we have to do some sabotage work, especially where the railroad is.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is, he says, it's a dangerous mission.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have to put in some explosive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And put them-- just put them, and then he is going to do with his men whatever worked out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we carried-- we had some bundles, you know, in Russian-- in camouflage bags.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
